    <div class="text-sm font-semibold mb-4">馃搳 鏁版嵁涓庨噷绋嬬</div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-3">
      <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700/50 border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-xl text-center">
