              <button type="button" class="app-image-ws-collect-btn" onclick="toggleAiwsFav()">
                <span aria-hidden="true">鈽?/span> <span id="aiws-collect-fav">0</span>
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="app-image-ws-collect-btn" onclick="toggleAiwsComments()">
                <span aria-hidden="true">馃挰</span> <span id="aiws-collect-comment">0</span>
              </button>
            </div>
            <div class="app-image-ws-tips">
              <div class="app-image-ws-tips-title">鍒涗綔灏忚创澹?/div>
              <div class="app-image-ws-tips-item">鉁?<span id="aiws-tip-success">杩戞湡杩愯鎴愬姛鐜囦负 95%</span></div>
              <div class="app-image-ws-tips-item">鈴?<span id="aiws-tip-duration">骞冲潎杩愯鏃堕暱绾?90s</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="app-image-ws-creator">
              <div class="app-image-ws-creator-info">
                <div class="app-image-ws-avatar" id="aiws-avatar" aria-hidden="true">
                  <span class="app-image-ws-avatar-emoji" id="aiws-avatar-emoji">馃</span>
                </div>
                <span class="app-image-ws-creator-name" id="aiws-creator-name">鍒涗綔鑰?/span>
              </div>
